Mick Moloney Irish-American Music and Popular Culture Field Recordings

New York Fleadh Cheoil. Comhaltas Ceoltóirí Éireann Fleadh Cheoil competition and session at Manhattan College, Bronx, NY. Competitors include: John Kennedy, Maureen Dowd, Andrew McDonald, Christopher Ever, John O'Rourke, Edward Boyle, Patricia Conway. Session musicians include: Brendan Mulvihill, Martin Mulvihill, Owen Thomas, Mary O'Callaghan, Keith O'Neill (fiddles), Tom O'Brien (flute), Margie Ford, Marie Tracy, Gail Mulvihill (banjos). (Four CDs – Total length: 01:47:52) aiamm80R, 81R, 82R, 83R
